				<wikidot:authorName>RecursiveRecursion</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1864349</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Probably because there’s no apparent way to predict who it will affect, other than putting <em>everyone</em> who’s ever been struck by lightning on a watchlist. Remember, Keter doesn’t (necessarily) mean ‘dangerous’, it means ‘it’s a real pain to contain and keep contained’.</p> 
				 	]]>
